data.meta_description:
Printed on certificate: Mrs. Lillie R. Parker, having paid ten dollars is a LIFE MEMBER of this Association, entitled to the rights and privileges thereof.

Printed at top of certificate: "I go for all sharing the privileges of the government who assist in bearing its burdens--by no means excluding women." - Abraham Lincoln.

The certificate is signed by Emma Smith DeVoe (president), Ellen Swinburn Leckenby (secretary), and Cora Smith Eaton (treasurer).
